
Adding sampleRule file used to validate User authorization based on unique id from auth frameowrk. 
The rules restrict write access to a database path to the authenticated user. 
Also added data validation rules for the Wifi and PowerState database fields. 

Apply the rule as:
	Firebase Console 
		--> Project 
			--> Realtime Database [from left pane]
				--> Rules 
					--> Edit rules 
						--> Publish!!
